Package: adaptiveFTS
Title: Adaptive Functional Time Series analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Hassan", "Maissoro", , "maissorohassan@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: 
  This package contains the adaptive estimation procedure proposed by Maissoro et al. (2024) for weakly dependent functional time series. 
  It implements the local regularity estimator, the mean function estimator and the autocovariance function estimator.
